list.name: container start time
list.rawQuery:
SELECT
  start_date as time,
  container_id,
  test_id
FROM
  jmeter_metrics.container
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("start_date")

list.name: container end time
list.rawQuery:
SELECT
  end_date as time,
  container_id,
  test_id
FROM
  jmeter_metrics.container
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("end_date")

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  sum(count) AS "count"
FROM jmeter_metrics.sample_metric
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(timestamp) AND
  (-9999 in (${testId:sqlstring}) OR test_id in (${testId:sqlstring})) AND
  ('%%all%%' in (${location:sqlstring}) OR location IN (${location:sqlstring})) AND
  not is_transaction

SELECT "error".sum::decimal / "all".sum
FROM

     WHERE

             ('%%all%%' in (${location:sqlstring}) OR location IN (${location:sqlstring})) AND
             not is_transaction) as "all",
    (SELECT sum(count) as sum from jmeter_metrics.sample_error_metric
     WHERE

             (-9999 in (${testId:sqlstring}) OR test_id in (${testId:sqlstring})) AND
             ('%%all%%' in (${location:sqlstring}) OR location IN (${location:sqlstring})) AND
             not is_transaction) as "error";

SELECT 
  at.time + interval '${aggregation_interval}s' as time, 
  sum(at.threads) as "Threads",
  concat('Threads ', test_id)
FROM (
  SELECT time_bucket('${aggregation_interval}s', "timestamp") as time,
  locf(last(threads, timestamp)) as "threads",
  test_id
  FROM jmeter_metrics.thread_metric
  WHERE
  $__timeFilter(timestamp) AND
  (-9999 in (${testId:sqlstring}) OR test_id in (${testId:sqlstring})) AND
  ('%%all%%' in (${location:sqlstring}) OR location IN (${location:sqlstring}))
  GROUP BY 1, container_id, test_id
  ORDER BY 1
) at
GROUP BY 1, test_id
ORDER BY 1

FROM (SELECT  time_bucket('${aggregation_interval}s', "timestamp") as time,

WITH test_1_transaction_total AS (SELECT thread_group_name,
                                         name,
                                         sum(count) AS "count"
                                  FROM jmeter_metrics.sample_metric
                                  WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
                                    AND (-9999 in (${testId:sqlstring}) OR test_id in (${testId:sqlstring}))
                                    AND ('%%all%%' in (${location:sqlstring}) OR location IN (${location:sqlstring}))
                                    AND is_transaction
                                  GROUP BY thread_group_name, name),
     test_1_transaction_failed AS (SELECT thread_group_name,
                                          name,
                                          sum(count) AS "count"
                                   FROM jmeter_metrics.sample_error_metric
                                   WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
                                     AND (-9999 in (${testId:sqlstring}) OR test_id in (${testId:sqlstring}))
                                     AND ('%%all%%' in (${location:sqlstring}) OR location IN (${location:sqlstring}))
                                     AND is_transaction
                                   GROUP BY thread_group_name, name)
SELECT t1.thread_group_name             AS "Thread Group Name",
       t1.name                          AS "Transaction",
       t1.count                         AS "Transaction total count",
       t1.count - COALESCE(t2.count, 0) AS "Transaction success count",
       COALESCE(t2.count, 0)            AS "Transaction failed count"
FROM test_1_transaction_total t1
LEFT JOIN test_1_transaction_failed t2
  ON t1.thread_group_name = t2.thread_group_name
 AND t1.name = t2.name;

                                    AND ('%%all%%' in (${location:sqlstring}) OR location IN (${location:sqlstring}))

     test_1_transaction_failed AS (SELECT thread_group_name,

                                     AND ('%%all%%' in (${location:sqlstring}) OR location IN (${location:sqlstring}))
                                     AND not is_transaction
                                   GROUP BY thread_group_name, name)

LEFT JOIN test_1_transaction_failed t2

 AND t1.name = t2.name;

with error_metric as (SELECT thread_group_name,
                             name,
                             sum(count) as count
                      FROM jmeter_metrics.sample_error_metric
                      WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
                        AND (-9999 in (${testId:sqlstring}) OR test_id in (${testId:sqlstring})) 
                        AND ('%%all%%' in (${location:sqlstring}) OR location IN (${location:sqlstring}))
                      GROUP BY thread_group_name, name),
     error_detail as (SELECT thread_group_name,
                             name,
                             response_code,
                             response_message
                      FROM jmeter_metrics.sample_error_detail
                      WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
                        AND (-9999 in (${testId:sqlstring}) OR test_id in (${testId:sqlstring})) 
                        AND ('%%all%%' in (${location:sqlstring}) OR location IN (${location:sqlstring}))
                        AND  response_code is not null
                      GROUP BY thread_group_name, name, response_code, response_message)
select em.thread_group_name as "Thread Group Name",
       em.name as "Transaction",
       em.count,
       ed.response_code,
       ed.response_message
from error_metric em
left join error_detail ed
  on em.thread_group_name = ed.thread_group_name
 and em.name = ed.name;

SELECT 
  time + interval '${aggregation_interval}s' as time,
  "usage_percent",
  "metric"
FROM (
  SELECT time_bucket('${aggregation_interval}s', "time") as time,
  max(100 - usage_idle) as "usage_percent",
  concat('Test ', test_id, ' container ', container_id, ' ', cpu) as "metric"
  FROM test_runner_monitoring.cpu
  WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND
  (-9999 in (${testId:sqlstring}) OR test_id::integer in (${testId:sqlstring})) AND
  ('%%all%%' in (${location:sqlstring}) OR test_runner_location IN (${location:sqlstring})) AND
  cpu != 'cpu-total'
  GROUP BY 1, cpu, container_id, test_id 
  ORDER BY 1, 3
) sub

  sub.container as "metric"
FROM (
  SELECT 
    time_bucket('${aggregation_interval}s', "time") as time,
    max(used) as "used_total",
    concat('Test ', test_id, ' container ', container_id, ' usage total') as "container"
  FROM test_runner_monitoring.mem
  WHERE
    $__timeFilter(time) AND
    (-9999 in (${testId:sqlstring}) OR test_id::integer in (${testId:sqlstring})) AND
    ('%%all%%' in (${location:sqlstring}) OR test_runner_location IN (${location:sqlstring}))
  GROUP BY 1, container_id, test_id
  ORDER BY 1
) sub

SELECT 
  time + interval '${aggregation_interval}s' as time,
  "received",
  "container"
FROM (
  SELECT 
    time_bucket('${aggregation_interval}s', "time") as time,
    max(bytes_recv) - lag(max(bytes_recv)) OVER w as "received",
    container_id as "container"
  FROM test_runner_monitoring.net
  WHERE
    $__timeFilter(time) AND
    (-9999 in (${testId:sqlstring}) OR test_id::integer in (${testId:sqlstring})) AND
    ('%%all%%' in (${location:sqlstring}) OR test_runner_location IN (${location:sqlstring})) AND
    interface = 'eth0'
  GROUP BY 1, container_id
  WINDOW w as (PARTITION BY container_id ORDER BY time_bucket('${aggregation_interval}s', "time"))
) sub

SELECT 
  time + interval '${aggregation_interval}s' as time,
  "sent",
  "container"
FROM (
  SELECT 
    time_bucket('${aggregation_interval}s', "time") as time,
    max(bytes_sent) - lag(max(bytes_sent)) OVER w as "sent",
    container_id as "container"
  FROM test_runner_monitoring.net
  WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND
  (-9999 in (${testId:sqlstring}) OR test_id::integer in (${testId:sqlstring})) AND
  ('%%all%%' in (${location:sqlstring}) OR test_runner_location IN (${location:sqlstring})) AND
  interface = 'eth0'
  GROUP BY 1, container_id
  WINDOW w as (PARTITION BY container_id ORDER BY time_bucket('${aggregation_interval}s', "time"))
) sub

SELECT 
  time + interval '${aggregation_interval}s' as time,
  "read",
  "container"
FROM (
  SELECT 
    time_bucket('${aggregation_interval}s', "time") as time,
    max(read_bytes) - lag(max(read_bytes)) OVER w as "read",
    concat(container_id, ' ', name) as "container"
  FROM test_runner_monitoring.diskio
  WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND
  (-9999 in (${testId:sqlstring}) OR test_id::integer in (${testId:sqlstring})) AND
  ('%%all%%' in (${location:sqlstring}) OR test_runner_location IN (${location:sqlstring}))
  GROUP BY 1, container_id, name
  WINDOW w as (PARTITION BY container_id, name ORDER BY time_bucket('${aggregation_interval}s', "time")) 
  ORDER BY 1
) sub

SELECT 
  time + interval '${aggregation_interval}s' as time,
  "written",
  "container"
FROM (
  SELECT 
    time_bucket('${aggregation_interval}s', "time") as "time",
    max(write_bytes) - lag(max(write_bytes)) OVER w as "written",
    concat(container_id, ' ', name) as "container"
  FROM test_runner_monitoring.diskio
  WHERE
    $__timeFilter(time) AND
    (-9999 in (${testId:sqlstring}) OR test_id::integer in (${testId:sqlstring})) AND
    ('%%all%%' in (${location:sqlstring}) OR test_runner_location IN (${location:sqlstring}))
  GROUP BY 1, container_id, name
  WINDOW w as (PARTITION BY container_id, name ORDER BY time_bucket('${aggregation_interval}s', "time"))
  ORDER BY 1
) sub
